concept_explanation.lcs:
**Longest Common Subsequence — 2D DP:**

```java
// dp[i][j] = LCS length of s1[0..i-1] and s2[0..j-1]
int[][] dp = new int[m+1][n+1];
for(int i=1;i<=m;i++) for(int j=1;j<=n;j++) {
    if(s1.charAt(i-1)==s2.charAt(j-1))
        dp[i][j]=dp[i-1][j-1]+1;    // match: extend
    else
        dp[i][j]=Math.max(dp[i-1][j],dp[i][j-1]); // skip one
}
// dp[m][n] = LCS length
// O(mn) time, O(mn) space (or O(n) with rolling rows)
```

concept_explanation.edit_distance:
**Edit Distance — 3 operations:**

```java
// dp[i][j] = min edits to convert s1[0..i-1] to s2[0..j-1]
// Operations: insert, delete, replace (all cost 1)
for(int i=1;i<=m;i++) for(int j=1;j<=n;j++) {
    if(s1.charAt(i-1)==s2.charAt(j-1))
        dp[i][j]=dp[i-1][j-1];              // same char: no cost
    else
        dp[i][j]=1+Math.min(dp[i-1][j-1],  // replace
                   Math.min(dp[i-1][j],     // delete from s1
                            dp[i][j-1]));   // insert into s1
}
```
